Class TGRequest<T extends TGResponse>

  • java.lang.Object

    Comparable<com.android.volley.Request<T>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    TGJsonRequest, TGStringRequest

    public abstract class TGRequest<T extends TGResponse>
extends com.android.volley.Request<T>
    TGRequest has been created on top of strong Volley framework. TGRequest encapsulates all the hurdle of network calls and enables clean object orientated approach to the service caller.
